 ProtoOrder — Prototyping Services Platform
A full-stack e-commerce platform for electronics prototyping services — built, deployed, and maintained in production.
   
________________________________________
What It Does
A production-grade web platform that allows customers to place online orders for electronics prototyping services — including PCB board manufacturing, 3D printing, laser cutting, and electronics project development.
Customers upload their design files, preview them interactively, select quantities, and complete payment — all in one place. The platform supports multiple file uploads in a single order, which most competitor platforms do not offer.
________________________________________
❗ Problem It Solves
The company was previously accepting orders only offline, forcing customers to visit in person. This limited reach, slowed order processing, and made scaling impossible.
This platform moved the entire ordering workflow online — bringing the business to customers instead of the other way around.
________________________________________
🛠 Tech Stack
Layer	Technology
Frontend	React, TypeScript, JavaScript
Backend	Node.js, REST APIs
Database	MySQL, Prisma ORM
Payments	Razorpay (UPI, cards, netbanking)
Auth	Google OAuth, Email/Password

File Handling	Multi-file upload, Gerber viewer, 3D model viewer
Deployment	Hostinger (live & maintained)
Other	Python (file processing utilities)
________________________________________
🏗 System Architecture
Customer Browser
      │
      ▼
  React Frontend (TypeScript)
      │
      ├── File Upload (Gerber / STL / DXF files)
      ├── Gerber Viewer (PCB preview with 0.1mm accuracy)
      ├── 3D Model Viewer (360° preview)
      └── Order & Payment UI
      │
      ▼
  Node.js Backend (REST APIs)
      │
      ├── Authentication (Google OAuth + Email/Password)
      ├── Order Management
      ├── File Processing (Python utilities)
      └── Razorpay Payment Gateway
      │
      ▼
   MySQL Database (via Prisma ORM)
      │
      ▼
  Hostinger (Live Deployment)
________________________________________
 Key Features
•	Multi-file ordering — upload multiple design files with individual quantities in one order (unique vs competitors)
•	Gerber file viewer — interactive PCB preview with precise 0.1mm dimension accuracy
•	3D model viewer — 360° rotation so customers verify designs before manufacturing
•	Razorpay integration — UPI, netbanking, debit/credit cards, account transfer
•	Dual authentication — Google OAuth and email/password login
•	Admin dashboard — order tracking, status updates, customer management
•	Live and maintained — actively running in production with real customers
________________________________________
 My Role
I was the sole developer on this project during my internship. My responsibilities included:
•	Designed and built the complete system architecture from scratch
•	Developed the full backend — REST APIs, database schema, business logic
•	Built the React + TypeScript frontend — all pages, components, and user flows
•	Integrated Razorpay payment gateway — handling all payment modes
•	Built the custom Gerber file viewer with 0.1mm rendering accuracy
•	Integrated 3D model viewer for pre-order design verification
•	Set up Google OAuth and email/password authentication
•	Deployed the application on Hostinger and configured the server
•	Currently actively maintaining the live system — monitoring, bug fixes, and updates
________________________________________
 Deployment
The platform is live and in production, serving real customers for a prototyping services company in India.
This is a private commercial project. Source code is not publicly available, but I am happy to walk through the architecture and implementation in detail during interviews.
